genresAdvancedInfo.name: urban kiz
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Urban kiz is a modern African dance music genre that originated in Angola and has spread throughout the world. It combines elements of traditional kizomba with urban and electronic music, creating a sensual and energetic sound that is perfect for dancing. Urban kiz is characterized by its syncopated rhythms, melodic hooks, and smooth vocals. Its lyrics often deal with love, relationships, and the joys and challenges of city life. Urban kiz has become a popular dance style in clubs and festivals around the globe.
